caption: The image is a festive illustration of a tiger wearing a hat and holding a gold ingot. The tiger is surrounded by a pile of doughnuts, with some of them being golden in color. The scene is set against a red background, which is a traditional color for Chinese New Year celebrations. The image is captioned "Happy Chinese New Year" and "Wishing you good health and fortune in 2022".
original_title: Happy Chinese New Year Instagram Story Celebration Lunar Tiger 2022
texts:
Wishing you good health 
and fortune in 2022
